    <section class="module content">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 style="text-align:center; font-size:60px">What Are CubeSats?</h1>
            <hr>
            <p>CubeSats, or as we like to call them "cute sats", are small satelites coming in 10 cm x 10 cm x 10 cm units weighing about 1.33 kg. A satelite can consist of up to 12 units; no bigger than a shoebox! CubeSats are grouped under the umbrella category of nanosatellites as their total masses are under 500 kg.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

