                        </div>
                        <div class="card__back">
                            <span class="card__text">CubeSats can be sent out in swarms, each CubeSat having a seperate function, and work togethor to research one objective. Different CubeSats can be looking at different parts of the spectrum, for example, but be gathering data to accomplish the same goal. Losing one or two CubeSats, which are relatively cheap, in a swarm won't have as big as an impact of losing functionality on one large satellite.</span>
